name: Yankee
overview: On the run from the police, an Arizona man crosses into Mexico and gets deeply involved in drug trafficking, with the help of modern technology.

episodes.name: The Flight of Aeschylus
episodes.overview: Real estate agent and drug smuggler Malcolm gets into trouble after an altercation at his house and must flee Arizona, crossing into Mexico.

episodes.name: Aberrations
episodes.overview: Malcolm shows Cara Sucia a new way to smuggle drugs across the border. Sheriff Valenzuela and Agent Wolf each independently look into Malcolm.

episodes.name: Belize
episodes.overview: Yvonne helps Malcolm, now Yankee, meet with his brother, who has a plan for his escape. Cara Sucia punishes his men. Wolf finds a source in Mexico.

episodes.name: The Golden Hour
episodes.overview: Wolf's life is put in danger. Cara Sucia offers to introduce Yankee to Choche, so long as he follows his violent orders. Del Toro strikes a deal.

episodes.name: The Eagles
episodes.overview: Choche gives Yankee more responsibility, much to Cara Sucia's and Piporro's chagrin. Wolf is assigned a crucial mission. Phoebe suffers financial woes.
Yankee meets influential cartel boss El Botas. Cara Sucia starts extorting store owners and Parra takes note. Piporro's violence brings consequences.

episodes.name: Pen√©lope in Puerto Pe√±asco
episodes.overview: Cara Sucia mourns his loss and swears vengeance. Phoebe and Yankee reunite in Mexico and discuss their future. Fidelia brings Wolf along on a job.

episodes.name: Midday Cowboy
episodes.overview: Phoebe makes a startling decision. Despite Choche's orders, Yankee seeks revenge on Cara Sucia. La Contra takes control of Clandestina nightclub.

episodes.name: Operation Serpent
episodes.overview: A coordinated attack on Choche and his men takes them by surprise, and Del Toro uses it to his advantage. Yankee worries about his family.

episodes.name: Frauds
episodes.overview: Wolf offers help to a desperate Yankee. La Contra's violence escalates and Cara Sucia goes after Las Aguilas. Phoebe hires a new employee, Brian.

episodes.name: Mr. Lucky
episodes.overview: Parra asks El Botas to turn Yankee in. Revueltas's daughter is kidnapped. Cara Sucia's ambition grows and Del Toro is put in danger.

episodes.name: Rookies
episodes.overview: Back in Arizona, Yankee plots revenge with Wolf's help. Phoebe gets more involved in the drug business. Las Aguilas use technology to their advantage.

episodes.name: Reunion and Betrayal
episodes.overview: Las Aguilas' espionage techniques help uncover Parra's location. Wolf gives ICE crucial information. Yankee suffers a shocking betrayal.

episodes.name: Overboard
episodes.overview: Cara Sucia's act of narcoterrorism shocks Yankee and Revueltas. ICE interrogates Parra. Billy asks Valenzuela for his job back and seeks revenge.

episodes.name: Collateral Damage
episodes.overview: Yankee is shaken by the execution of one of his employees. Del Toro investigates both the attempt made on his life and the casino fire.

episodes.name: An Honest Officer
episodes.overview: Wolf meets with one of the fire's survivors. Confined to the hospital, Yankee thinks about revenge and misses his family. Valenzuela meets with Phoebe.

episodes.name: Beginner Horses
episodes.overview: Cara Sucia celebrates his terrorism. Yankee proposes a radical idea to Revueltas and Botas that involves an unexpected collaboration.

episodes.name: Every Day There's War
episodes.overview: Citizens protest against La Contra and violence ensues. Cara Sucia targets Del Toro's family. Yankee starts working with the authorities.

episodes.name: Eagles and Serpents
episodes.overview: La Contra's enemies -- including Mexican and American authorities plus Yankee -- go after the cartel in a large-scale operation.

episodes.name: Local Heroes
episodes.overview: Yankee makes Ignacio a difficult offer while also attempting to help Amelia. Cara Sucia targets his rival's drones with a winged friend.

episodes.name: The Ocean Is a Desert
episodes.overview: Phoebe realizes she sold guns to La Contra and Yankee decides to use it to their advantage. Del Toro sets his sights on Cara Sucia.

episodes.name: Pax Romana
episodes.overview: With the marines under suspicion, Del Toro investigates Diana de la Hoya's murder. Yvonne and Yankee make a peace deal. Wolf's trauma haunts her.

episodes.name: Resurrection
episodes.overview: Yankee has serious concerns about his family's safety in light of his discovery. Wolf is suspicious about La Contra's actions.

episodes.name: Kibbitz
episodes.overview: In a large meeting with Mexico's narcos, Yankee suggests adding fentanyl to the drug trade and offers up a deal with Wolf.

episodes.name: Happiness Is a Rebellion
episodes.overview: Yankee and Phoebe decide how to handle their future, which hinges on his relationship with Amelia. Yvonne makes a power play. Billy chooses violence.
